Each Enemy object should contain a pointer to an array of structures.  These structures should contain a pointer to each Ally and an integer holding a value of how much enmity that Ally has earned.

Mob parties should have strategic intelligence and be capable of coordinated attacks

Some mobs (at this point called "mirror" mobs) should, in addition to the ablilities inherent in thier class makeup, have the abilty to use their current target's abilities.
